  "description": "<p><strong>据经济之声报道，知情人士7月24日向记者爆料，深圳龙华富士康消费电子产品事业群（CCPBG事业群）在前一天集体停工。虽然富士康新闻发言人对记者否认，但记者昨晚获得当日停工的独家照片和视频。</strong>7月23日早上9点，富士康深圳龙华园区，大约200多位白班员工参与停工，这些员工从消费电子产品事业群（富士康内部简称：CP）工作区D4栋3楼走到工会总部，途中员工边走边喊口号要求加工资。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f2514e4/sc/6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246032.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%A0%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E2%80%9D%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5+%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%8A%E7%BB%99%E7%AD%94%E5%A4%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246032.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%A0%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E2%80%9D%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5+%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%8A%E7%BB%99%E7%AD%94%E5%A4%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246032.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%A0%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E2%80%9D%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5+%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%8A%E7%BB%99%E7%AD%94%E5%A4%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F246032.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%9B%A0%E2%80%9C%E5%B7%A5%E8%B5%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E2%80%9D%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5+%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E7%A7%B0%E4%BB%8A%E7%BB%99%E7%AD%94%E5%A4%8D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src